OL,4,Cangry customers with multiple bills a
OL,5,Cday
OL,7,FOne customer told ITV News' Consumer
OL,8,FEditor Chris Choi she has been living
OL,9,Fin fear of debt collectors after
OL,10,Freceiving incorrect bills to her home
OL,11,Faddress
OL,13,FWords by Deputy Content Editor Liz
OL,14,FLittle
OL,16,FAn ITV News investigation has
OL,17,Funcovered extreme cases of customer
OL,18,Fservice failures by British Gas. One
OL,19,Fcustomer received dozens of bills a
OL,20,Fday, more than 300 over a couple of
OL,21,Fmonths.
