OL,7,FAnother had their credit score
OL,8,Fdestroyed over erroneous billing
OL,9,Fissues. We've found that that when
OL,10,Fthese customers complained to British
OL,11,FGas service agents, they were advised
OL,12,Fthat their problems were affected by
OL,13,Fthe move of their accounts onto a new
OL,14,Fbilling system.
