OL,7,FHe told ITV News the hardest thing
OL,8,F"was getting anyone to listen" - but
OL,9,Fwhen he finally did get a customer
OL,10,Fagent on the phone, they blamed the
OL,11,Fissue on the process of moving to the
OL,12,Fnew billing system, which they call
OL,13,F"migration".
OL,15,FIn a phone call he recorded, a
OL,16,Fcustomer agent says to Shaun Stott,
OL,17,F"to be honest it sounds like it's just
OL,18,Fbeen part of the migration issue that
OL,19,Fwe have been struggling with".
