OL,7,FBritish Gas told ITV News the call
OL,8,Fhandler was wrong to blame migration,
OL,9,Fsaying Ann Adam's account has not even
OL,10,Fswitched to the new billing system.
OL,11,FHowever, some of the 212 accounts
OL,12,Fwhich have been incorrectly billed to
OL,13,FAnn's address may have moved to it.
OL,15,FAnn is still receiving incorrect bills
OL,16,Fto her home address, even though she
OL,17,Fleft British Gas in April.
