OL,7,FBritish Gas customer Alison Greenough
OL,8,Fwas also told by a one of the
OL,9,Fcompany's customer agents that her
OL,10,Faccount issues were affected by
OL,11,Fmigration.
OL,13,FAlison was preparing to remortgage her
OL,14,Ffamily home in January when she
OL,15,Fdiscovered her excellent credit score
OL,16,Fhad been demolished by problems with a
OL,17,FBritish Gas direct debit.
