OL,7,FShe contacted the firm daily to
OL,8,Fresolve the issue, but due to delays
OL,9,Fin hearing back from customer service,
OL,10,Fshe missed the chance to secure a
OL,11,Fbetter mortgage rate. Alison had to
OL,12,Faccept a loan on a far higher
OL,13,Frepayments, which she says has cost
OL,14,Fher more than #7,000.
