OL,7,FWhile researching British Gas customer
OL,8,Fservice experiences, ITV news was
OL,9,Fcontacted by a former call handler on
OL,10,Fthe condition of anonymity. They
OL,11,Fclaimed that there are issues with the
OL,12,Fmigration process and called on the
OL,13,FEnergy Ombudsman to investigate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
