OL,7,FThe Ombudsman added: "British Gas has
OL,8,Fbeen open with us about the steps it
OL,9,Fis taking to address any issues it has
OL,10,Fexperienced during the migration and
OL,11,Fhas confirmed that it has put
OL,12,Fsolutions in place to resolve and fix
OL,13,Fthese issues."
OL,15,FITV News contacted British Gas about
OL,16,Four investigation. They responded:
OL,17,F"When we make mistakes, we hold our
OL,18,Fhands up, we make it right and we
OL,19,Flearn from them because we care about
OL,20,Four service and we care about our
OL,21,Fcustomers.
