OL,7,F"In these unconnected cases of Ms
OL,8,FAdams and Ms Greenough, we made
OL,9,Fmistakes and we're sorry for that.
OL,10,FThese are isolated cases, but we'll
OL,11,Flearn from it to continue to improve
OL,12,Four customer service.
OL,14,F"We appreciate this has been
OL,15,Ffrustrating and we're sorry we've let
OL,16,Fthose customers down and grateful to
OL,17,FITV for bringing these mistakes to our
OL,18,Fattention."
